<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1 class="headertext">About Daymaker Digital</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "me.jpg", width: '100%', alt: "profile image" %>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="col-md-1"></div> -->
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Our mission statement drives our company and keeps us focused on the things that truly matter. Every company means start-ups, industry leaders, or mom-and-pop shops. We believe that the size of your budget shouldn't dictate the quality of your presence.</p>
        <p>Beautiful design tells the story of your brand, boldly and honestly. Our work will always seek to engage an audience and build community. We believe that good design is user-centered design, meaning that we keep real people at the center of everything we do.</p>
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#skillsCard"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="skillsCard"
          >
            Skills
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobhistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="skillsCard">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="skills">
                <h2>Skills</h2>
                <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                  <div class="skill">
                    <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                    <div class="progress">
                      <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                            role="progressbar"
                            aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utelized %>"
                            aria-valuemax="100"
                            style="width: <%= skill.percent_utelized %>%"
                            >
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <h2>Job History</h2>
              <div class="about-list-item">
                Jobbbbbbbbbbsssssssssss
              </div>
              <div class="about-list-item">
                Jobbbbbbbbbbsssssssssss
              </div>
              <div class="about-list-item">
                Jobbbbbbbbbbsssssssssss
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <h2>Education</h2>
              <div class="about-list-item">
                College PSU
              </div>
              <div class="about-list-item">
                Emergency MGMT
              </div>
              <div class="about-list-item">
                TeaLeaf Academy Ruby on Rails
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
